290
00:23:40,950 --> 00:23:43,420
[Shang]

291
00:23:53,490 --> 00:23:53,860
Gosh.

292
00:23:53,860 --> 00:23:54,460
Ouch!

293
00:23:54,530 --> 00:23:54,900
Ouch!

294
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:57,230
Gosh.

295
00:23:57,430 --> 00:23:58,020
