302
00:24:04,740 --> 00:24:05,790
How could you say that?

303
00:24:05,980 --> 00:24:07,540
You hit me first.

304
00:24:07,740 --> 00:24:08,620
Even if you're not a thief,

305
00:24:08,620 --> 00:24:09,700
