558
00:37:47,340 --> 00:37:47,920
Ouch!

559
00:37:50,080 --> 00:37:51,480
You have an ulterior motive.

560
00:37:51,730 --> 00:37:52,660
I'm really fine.

561
00:37:52,800 --> 00:37:53,640
Nonsense.

562
00:37:54,040 --> 00:37:55,190
